.  SOURCE CODE FOR THE XE VERSION OF THE SIC FAMILY OF COMPUTER
.  This tests NOBASE, indirect addressing (ex: @VALUE), format 1 (ex: FIX)
TEST2    START   0
         LDB    #TABLE
         BASE    TABLE
         LDA     @VALUE
         NOBASE
         FIX
         RSUB
VALUE    WORD    5
TABLE    RESW    1
         END     TEST2